 data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ntsb-nhtsa-letter-tesla-210752970.html"><ins>敦促 NHTSA 对自动驾驶颁布更严格的法规</ins></a>，并在信中表示，“特斯拉正在公共道路上测试高度自动化的自动驾驶技术，但监督或报告要求有限。”</p><p>特斯拉专有的自动驾驶技术旨在在车辆车道内进行转向、加速和制动，而增强的系统则有助于在高速公路上变换车道。特斯拉表示，该系统并不是真正的自动化，需要人工的积极监督。该公司尚未回应<em>路透社</em>就这起最新事故和新启动的调查发表评论的请求。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/tesla-faces-fresh-safety-probe-following-fatal-accident-180725262.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/tesla-faces-fresh-safety-probe-following-fatal-accident-180725262.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 104b025b-d4c1-483f-b7dd-27f2ca9b7dcc</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 10 Aug 2023 18:07:25 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691690552</ingested><modified> 2023-08-10T18:02:38+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Automotive Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[Transport Accident]]></category><category><![CDATA[Transportation]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="4614" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-images/2020-03/4ff3bce0-7036-11ea-9fbe-c57cab04a50c" width="6913"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="4614" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-images/2020-03/4ff3bce0-7036-11ea-9fbe-c57cab04a50c" width="6913"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDA